@startuml MCP Server - Deployment View
title MCP Server 部署视图 (Deployment View)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

skinparam node {
    BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    BorderColor #1976D2
}

' =============================================
' 场景1: Claude Desktop 集成
' =============================================

node "User Machine" as UserNode {
    component "Claude Desktop\n(GUI Application)" as ClaudeApp
    component "mcpserver.exe\n(子进程)" as McpExe1
    component "config.json" as Config1
    component "logs/" as Logs1
}

ClaudeApp --> McpExe1 : stdin (LSP Request)
McpExe1 --> ClaudeApp : stdout (LSP Response)
McpExe1 --> Config1 : read
McpExe1 --> Logs1 : write

note right of UserNode
    <b>STDIO 部署模式</b>
    • Claude Desktop 启动 mcpserver
    • 通过 stdin/stdout 通信
    • LSP 格式 (Content-Length 头)
    • 父进程管理子进程生命周期
end note

' =============================================
' 场景2: Web 客户端 (HTTP)
' =============================================

cloud "Network" as Internet {
    component "HTTP :8080" as HTTPPort
}

node "Server Machine" as ServerNode {
    component "mcpserver\n(HTTP Mode)" as McpExe2
    database "config.json" as Config2
    folder "logs/" as Logs2
}

node "Web Client Machine" as WebClientNode {
    component "Browser / Web App" as WebApp
}

WebApp --> Internet : HTTP POST\n(JSON-RPC)
Internet --> McpExe2
McpExe2 --> Internet : JSON Response
Internet --> WebApp

McpExe2 --> Config2 : read
McpExe2 --> Logs2 : write

note right of ServerNode
    <b>HTTP 部署模式</b>
    • 监听 0.0.0.0:8080
    • 线程池处理并发请求
    • 可配置端点和认证
    • 独立进程运行
end note

' =============================================
' 场景3: 混合部署 (BOTH Mode)
' =============================================

node "Hybrid Server" as HybridNode {
    component "mcpserver\n(BOTH Mode)" as McpExe3
    component "HTTP Thread\n(Background)" as HTTPThread
    component "STDIO Thread\n(Main)" as STDIOThread
    component "Shared JSON-RPC" as SharedJR
}

component "Claude Desktop" as ClaudeHybrid
component "Web Clients" as WebHybrid

ClaudeHybrid --> STDIOThread : stdin/stdout
WebHybrid --> HTTPThread : HTTP :8080

STDIOThread --> SharedJR : LSP → JSON
HTTPThread --> SharedJR : HTTP → JSON
SharedJR --> STDIOThread : JSON → LSP
SharedJR --> HTTPThread : JSON → HTTP

note right of HybridNode
    <b>BOTH 部署模式</b>
    • HTTP: 后台线程
    • STDIO: 主线程
    • 共享 JSON-RPC 处理器
    • 同时服务两种客户端
end note

' =============================================
' 资源访问 (下游系统)
' =============================================

node "External Resources" as ResNode {
    database "File System" as FS
    component "System APIs" as SysAPI
    component "User Functions\n(Custom Handlers)" as UserFunc
}

McpExe1 --> FS : Resource Read
McpExe2 --> FS : Resource Read
McpExe3 --> FS : Resource Read

McpExe1 --> SysAPI : Tool Execute
McpExe2 --> SysAPI : Tool Execute
McpExe3 --> SysAPI : Tool Execute

McpExe1 --> UserFunc : Custom Logic
McpExe2 --> UserFunc : Custom Logic
McpExe3 --> UserFunc : Custom Logic

' =============================================
' 网络配置
' =============================================

note bottom of Internet
    <b>网络配置:</b>
    • 协议: HTTP/1.1
    • 端口: 8080 (默认可配置)
    • 路径: POST /
    • 选项: SSE 支持
end note

' =============================================
' 部署架构说明
' =============================================

'note top of diagram
'    <b>三种部署模式对比:</b>
'
'    <b>STDIO:</b> 适合 Claude Desktop 等桌面应用
'    <b>HTTP:</b> 适合 Web 服务和多客户端场景
'    <b>BOTH:</b> 同时支持两种客户端
'end note

legend right
    |<back:back: #E8F5E9> 绿色 | 客户端机器 |
    |<back:back: #FFF3E0> 橙色 | HTTP 服务器 |
    |<back:back: #C8E6C9> 青色 | Web 客户端 |
    |<back:back: #F3E5F5> 紫色 | 混合模式服务器 |
    |<back:back: #FFE0B2> 深橙色 | 外部资源 |
    |<back:back: #E0F2F1> 青色 | 基础设施 |
    |<back:back: #BBDEFB> 浅蓝色 | 网络层 |
endlegend

@enduml
